values:
Wherefore doest the river flow?  Why must it take me with it?  Today I cleaned out my toe jam with my fingernails.  And then, without washing my hands, I ate 2 PB&J sandwiches.  I like PB&J.  They are yummy!  Anyway, Coach Price rocks, because he cathces me skipping everytime I do it.  And I do it so much.  Sorry mom!  Whitney looked so beautiful today.  Her makeup was perfect.  She does a good job with it.  Ryan smelled like fesces wrapped in burnt hair today.  I have a crush on Steven Bennett.  I don't think he knows, but maybe he will figure it out someday.
I burnt myself today lighting my cigarette.  And then I lost my keys.  AGAIN!!!  I had put them on top of my car last night when I was getting out of the car.  This morning, they weren't there.  That sucks.  Oh well, mommy will have to buy me another copy.  I sure do love my 88 Honda civic.  But the keys are hard to keep up with.
So what's going on in your world?  I hate boys (except Steven).  The girls at my school are sooooooo mean.  They are 2-faced punks.  But then again, so am I. JK  I'm perfect!!!  Especially my face.  People don't understand me.  They think I'm conceited.  But I'm not.  I just have opinions.  They just happen to be humble but accurate.
I ran over a squirrel yesterday.  It was as big as a chipmunk.  I freaked out and then reversed the car, and hit my dad's car.  That stunk.  So I put it in forward, and ran over my sister's tricycle.  Rough day huh?
Chapel rocked yesterday.  It only lasted an hour and 15 min.  as opposed to spiritual emphasis week where chapel lasted 5 hours.  Yay!
I had tea spilled on me last night, all over me.  Thanks O'Charley's!  Good times.  Why me????  Why me????  Why does O'Charley hate me???  Oh well.
Cliff is a sexy beast, but Colby is ugly!  Wait, they are twins.  Oh well, life is confusing.
Well, I'm off to lunch.  Love you guys!  Muah!!!
Haley

P.S.  fesces means poop.
P.S.S.  I weigh 84 lbs.  do I look fat?
P.S.S.S.  Soccer won yesterday, they are so good, I can't hit a ball with a bat like that, life stinks...

Today was good I guess...some STUPID band came to our school for a concert and it SUCKED..they didnt even sing! GAY...n*e*ways I am tryign to figure out why people say that they dont like some1 but then turn around and are BEST FRIENDS with them, its called being two faced and lately I have had a lot of my friends doin that..and its startin to PISS me off bad..N*E*WAYS..tomorrow my moms cooking CHOCOLATE CHIP MUFFINS! YAY!...too excited..I need the lyrics to "Some People Change" really badly. Well I will write more tomorrow! G2g for now
luv yall!

...Today went by pretty fast...this morning I had to come home from school for a while but uh I misses Mr.Hales class and Coach Prices...their classes are Soo0o boring..we got our report cards yesterday and I didnt have nt one C my mom was so0o proud of me..some poeple from school went to honduras today..they wont be back till March 5th..but thats fine with me becuz I dont like most of them..n*e*ways after school I came hoem and slept till Colby got off of work and then he came and we ate pizza and watched The Notebook by the way is the BEST love story EVER..I was about to say movie but the best movie is Saw..I cried watching The Notebook and of coarse Colby said that he didnt like it but whatever he knows he did..now Kyra is over here and we are just sittin here about to go to bed becuz I am so tired. Tomorrow I have to go to my lil sisters basketball game she cheers...and watch that but I think Whit is coming so itll be fun! lol..Whit didnt call me back by the way which sucks! Her and Brandon didnt do n*e*thing tongiht she said he ditched her probally for Kasi ugh, Colby has to work tomorrow and I doubt me and him will be able to do n*e*thing tomorrow night cuz he hasnt told his mom about his ticket yet and that sucks..but I am goin to sleep now..
nighty night

Hi you guys, Omg today was awesome I was in the best mood which usually NEVER happens..and I am SO Hyper..This morning I woke up and I thought I was gonna be lookin cute for school but I got out of the bed and said SCREW IT..and then slept for about 15 mor eminutes and then just threw on some pants and a hoodie..When I got to school I got in the back of Colby's car and SLEPT SOME MORE..lol.. When I saw Whitney this morning I felt better becuz my gosh Whit it's called SHOWER!! j/k In Algebra we did a whole lot of NOTHING as usual..and at Lunch Colby and Cory went and got me some uh Wendys! We got report cards today and I dont have one C...YAY NOT GROUNDED!...
After school Whitney came home with me and we watched Muary and then went to the tanning bed..then my mom said hey go get some Milk and a Dr.Peper..and so we went in Brunos with 5$ and we are gettin all that then my mom calls and says get some cotton balls and I dont hink I have enough money so we get to the cash register and NOPE NOT ENOUGH MONEY! Welp we go back to the car and get more money and go back in then as we are gettin gin the car I slam the Door on the Cotton Balls so they go EVERYWHERE! It was funny...well me and Whit are about to go get some Guthries and come home and eat then I am dropping her off at her house and then I am stopping by Colbys..
    With Love
Hale and Whit
